TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed beforefieldinit RandomGeneratorFactory extends Java.Lang.Object

Docs.summary: This is a factory class for generating multiple random number generators of a specific algorithm.

remarks.para: RandomGeneratorFactory also provides methods describing the attributes (or properties) of a generator and can be used to select random number generator algorithms. These methods are typically used in conjunction with RandomGeneratorFactory#all(). In this example, the code locates the RandomGeneratorFactory that produces RandomGenerator RandomGenerators with the highest number of state bits.
Added in 17.
